data.description: Fabulous updated farmhouse with something for everyone. This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has over 2400 sq ft of beautiful space. Situated on just over 2 acres you can enjoy your views of the wooded area right from your own deck. Updated kitchen with custom cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and mudroom. Separate living/dining room with open floor plan, family room, main floor master and additional sitting room/office space. Two car garage with extra parking space. Easy access to Hwy 270, and 367. Closr to shopping, schools and restaurants.
